plmxml_bus:SavedQueryDef.name: GET Dispatcher Requests
plmxml_bus:SavedQueryDef.Description: Query to get the Dispatcher Requests created for the Input Item Revisions

plmxml_bus:QueryClause.stringValue: SELECT qid FROM DispatcherRequest WHERE "ItemRevision:secondaryObjects.items_tag.item_id" = "${item_id = }" AND "ItemRevision:secondaryObjects.item_revision_id" = "${item_revision_id = }" AND "creation_date" >= "${Created After = }"
